metadata.name: #01 Ringing quiet
metadata.description:
"Mom, I'll be home late today for cram school."
Then she puts down the receiver.

In fact, I had called the cram school earlier to inform them of my absence.

Her straight black hair, the embodiment of a dignified woman, sways in the wind.
Her determined eyes look at me.
